\p
\v 54 'Ndirwirei Mwari, nezita renyu, Nditongerei nesimba renyu.
\p
\v 2 Inzwai munyengetero wangu,
\s Mwari;
\s Rerekerai nzeve yenyu munzwe mashoko omuromo wangu.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti vatorwa vakandimukira, Vamanikidzi vakatsvaka mweya
\s wangu.
\s Havana kuisa Mwari pamberi pavo.
\p
\v 4 Tarirai, Mwari ndiye mubatsiri wangu.
\s Ishe ari pakati pavanotsigira
\s mweya wangu.
\p
\v 5 Achatsiva zvakaipa kuvavengi vangu;
\s Muvaparadze nokutendeka kwenyu.
\p
\v 6 Ndichakubayirai nechipiriso chokungopa nokuzvidira,
\s Ndichavonga zita renyu, Jehovha, nokuti rakanaka.
\p
\v 7 Nokuti akandirwira
\s pakutambudzika kwose;
\s Ziso rangu rakaona kukundwa kwavavengi vangu.
